title: Collection of Animals
description: A collage featuring various animals, including birds, mammals, reptiles, and insects. The image is organized in a grid-like pattern, showcasing a diverse range of species such as eagles, bears, fish, and butterflies.

title: Illustration of a Penguin-like Bird
description: A beautifully detailed illustration of a bird resembling a penguin, swimming in water. The bird has a black and white plumage, with a distinctive beak holding a fish. In the background, there are rocky formations and other similar birds perched on the rocks, surrounded by aquatic plants.

title: Thylacine and Tasmanian Tiger
description: An illustration depicting two thylacines, also known as Tasmanian tigers, in a natural setting. One thylacine is standing upright, showcasing its distinctive striped back, while the other is lying down, also displaying similar stripes. The background features a landscape with vegetation typical of their habitat.
